Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.16,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,There is an emotion called fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.74,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very natural emotional\N reaction found in all animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:24.30,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Why does fear occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:30.31,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,There is the fear caused by animal instincts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:35.10,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,and the fear born of logical thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:40.61,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, when you encounter \Nsomething stronger than yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:43.83,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,and realize that you have no way of facing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:48.20,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,or when you encounter something unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:53.56,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Something as simple as\N "not knowing" can evoke fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:03.75,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,When faced with fear,\N you have a number of choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:10.30,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,You might struggle, resist, flee,\N accept, or many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:15.63,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,But upon meeting Lord DIO,\N a new reaction arises...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.50,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.14,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,How do people act once they feel joy in fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:31.88,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently on the plane\N that Joestar and the others are on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:38.01,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,They will not reach their destination safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.99,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,A... a rhinoceros beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:20.28,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.41,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A stag beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.33,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol, is that a Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Are we already encountering \Nanother Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:29.73,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It is very possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.05,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a bug-shaped Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It hid in the shadow of the seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:39.05,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.34,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo! It's on the side of your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.45,JoJo-MainTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.45,JoJo-MainTitle2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.92,JoJo-EpTitle,epi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,451)}Episode 4: Tower of Gray
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.40,JoJo-top,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's huge! It has to be a Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:25.33,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,That bug is a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:32.36,JoJo-Location,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.06,JoJo-top,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.84,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,But leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.43,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,B-Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:37.84,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard there is a user of a bug Stand \Nthat likes to rip out the tongues of its victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:39.88,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.43,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I-It dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.66,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:49.67,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It's faster than Star Platinum, \Nwhose speed and precision
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.72,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are such that it can grasp bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.91,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be a Stand.\N That bug is a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.73,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where is he hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.44,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the one who's controlling it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.65,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.13,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.87,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:10.87,JoJo-overlap,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.34,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, it could stop the spirit beetle's \Nmouth needle with its teeth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:26.26,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Since it tried to bite off Jotaro's Stand's tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.37,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It must be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.22,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The Tower card of the Tarot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.91,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The one that depicts a Stand suggesting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.23,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,destruction, calamity,\N and the end of a journey:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.73,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Tower of Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.99,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Tower of Gray commits mass murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,making them look like accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.14,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The airplane crash that happened last year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.34,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in England, causing 300 deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.62,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is thought to have been its work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:58.29,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I had heard rumors,\N but it seems he's working with DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.84,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I-It dodged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the single hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it also dodged a two-fisted rush of blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.83,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:22.29,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were to have ten guns\N shoot bullets from one centimeter away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.91,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,they would not be able to touch my Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:28.90,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,And you couldn't kill my \NStand with a bullet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.23,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.66,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the one controlling the Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of the passengers is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.71,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If we can track him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.18,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It moved over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.30,JoJo-internal/narrator,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What's it planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.11,JoJo-internal/narrator,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.85,JoJo-Crush,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.62,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.05,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Got their tongues!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.37,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,And my objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Massacre!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.78,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,This word's meaning: to kill everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.59,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-It actually did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.99,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I will burn it to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.26,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.12,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait a moment, Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.65,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,It's so noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what all the ruckus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:52.28,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.25,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.35,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,What's this slimy stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.50,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,M... A...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.68,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it blood?! Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.79,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Atemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:20.19,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,We have to defeat it before\N the other passengers panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.89,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,But, Avdol,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.73,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,an active Stand like your Magician's Red
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,could make the plane explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:33.03,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,And Jojo, if your power were to put a \Nhole in the fuselage, it'd be a catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.46,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,My quiet Stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:41.37,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hierophant Green,\N is most suited to defeating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.22,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Noriaki Kakyoin, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:48.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard all about you from Lord DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.37,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that your Stand is quiet, \Nthere's no point in challenging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:58.14,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot catch me with your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.68,JoJo-Fwish,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Fwish
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.68,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.56,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.36,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.47,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to think you can \Nhit me if you fire enough shots,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.45,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,but you haven't hit me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.87,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. It's still dodging with its speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.50,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.61,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,My speed is on an entirely different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.93,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too slow to get a bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.89,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,And Kakyoin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.30,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,With my next attack,\N I'll stab your Stand's tongue with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:49.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,this Tower Needle, and rip it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.97,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.98,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:00.57,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good!\N It dodged Emerald Splash again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:05.16,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,Once this rips your tongue out, you'll go mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.17,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,From the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What? If its tongue is ripped out,\N it'll go mad from the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.76,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} Hierophant Green?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.23,JoJo-main,tower,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.70,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If it rips {\i1}you{\i0} apart, it'll go mad, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.93,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,From joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:38.61,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hierophant's appendages had\N already slipped beneath the sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:43.83,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you realize I was trapping\N you there with Emerald Splash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.41,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,So that geezer was the user?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:05.81,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,A repulsive Stand usually has a repulsive user.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.94,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't appear that he has \NDIO's flesh bud in his forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:20.70,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,From the start, Tower of Gray was \N an evil Stand that killed tourists,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:24.07,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,making it look like an\N accident only in return for pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.53,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure DIO was able to \Nuse him because he was
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.00,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,easily bought, and blinded by greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.45,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.47,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I could be imagining it, but it seems\N like the plane is flying crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.17,JoJo-main,CA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.87,JoJo-main,CA,0000,0000,0000,,The cockpit is up ahead,\N so passengers may not enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.38,JoJo-main,CA,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.58,JoJo-internal/narrator,CA,0000,0000,0000,,My! What a handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.25,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Move, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.46,JoJo-main,CA,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.63,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.38,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:22.20,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It is inexcusable of him to treat \Nwomen in such a cruel manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.14,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:27.44,JoJo-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.10,JoJo-Bam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.05,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We've been had!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.73,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Their tongues have been ripped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.18,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,That stag beetle bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:40.41,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,He had already killed the pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.78,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.91,JoJo-main,jopseh,0000,0000,0000,,The autopilot's been destroyed, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This plane's going to crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.00,JoJo-Splat,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Splat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.71,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.61,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Stand that holds The Tower card
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.57,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,which suggests accidents \Nand the end of a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.73,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,You will not reach Lord DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:18.59,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you survive this crash,\N you are 10,000 kilometers from Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:25.25,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,Those who swore loyalty to Lord DIO\N will pursue you every hour of every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:30.95,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,There are Stands in this world \Nthat you can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:34.14,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO is the master of Stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:39.43,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO has the power to \Nreign over all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:42.09,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'll reach him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:46.55,JoJo-main,gray,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards will never reach Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.27,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:59.51,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing you didn't scream. \NThat would've been annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.86,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I've got a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.38,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,This old man is now going to\N emergency land this plane on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:10.41,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Go put life jackets and seat belts \Non all of the other passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.87,JoJo-main,CA,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:13.46,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:18.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I have experience \Nwith propeller planes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.17,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Propellers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:23.42,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But, Jotaro... this is my third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.10,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard of someone being in a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:30.15,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,crashing plane three times?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.56,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.27,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never riding in a plane with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.99,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(368,0)}Tower of Gray
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.99,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(877,0)}Gray Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:15:00.57,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,The plane landed 35 kilometers \Noff the Hong Kong coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:04.67,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro and the others had no \Nchoice but to head to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:04.61,JoJo-announcer,news,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a jumbo jet made an emergency landing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.76,JoJo-announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,35 kilometers south of Hong Kong,\N near Lamma Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.09,JoJo-announcer,news,0000,0000,0000,,Efforts are underway\N to rescue all passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:11.18,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Hong Kong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.64,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Hong Kong Island! Kowloon! The New Territories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:18.86,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,With more than 235 islands in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:21.55,JoJo-Location2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(462,464)}— Hong Kong —
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:23.11,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,the view of the area at night is\N known as the "Million Dollar View."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Right. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure the only\N ones aboard are us and the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:34.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We don't want any more victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.06,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.37,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.98,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Want some rice porridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.79,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in Hong Kong,\N you gotta try dim sum or rice porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.42,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,We have hot cola, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:50.04,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Rice porridge, eh? Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.69,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Jojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:56.43,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike in Japan, rice porridge\N is a staple food in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:01.00,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have it the popular way,\N with pork and a century egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.15,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.33,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.48,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:07.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys trying to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go to my friend's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:15.04,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dandy guy. Want to try \Nsome Hong Kong hot cola?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.44,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows that\N cola's supposed to be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.98,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, who were you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:27.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh, I'll explain everything\Nwhen we get to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:35.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We need to work out a plan that'll get us \Nto Egypt as safely and quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.76,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:43.39,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar, we cannot allow any \Nmore innocent civilians to be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.31,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The quickest way would be by plane, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:52.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now become impossible\N for us to fly to Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:57.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If we encounter another Stand user\N like the last one on a commercial flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:02.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,we're sure to cause a disaster\Nthat will harm many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.96,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to get to Egypt by either land or sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:11.96,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But if we fail to meet DIO within fifty days...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.72,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If we had stayed on that plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.22,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd probably be in Cairo by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.93,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.23,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too soon to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:36.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred years ago,\N Jules Verne wrote a story in which
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.22,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the protagonist traveled around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.54,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in 80 days, traveling 40,000 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:43.37,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That was in the age of trains and steamboats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.78,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Even without a plane, in fifty days,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to travel\N the 10,000 kilometers to Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,As for the route...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I say we go by sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We'll charter a suitably-sized boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:02.90,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,go around the Malay peninsula, \Nand cross the Indian Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.98,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the Silk Road of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.91,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that is best, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.98,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,If we go by land, borders will be a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.36,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,And we'd have to cross\N the Himalayas and a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.70,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,If we ran into trouble,\N we'd lose a great deal of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.07,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.77,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to any of\N those places using either route,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.04,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.08,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it up to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.33,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest danger will be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Stand users that DIO sends against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to do our best to get \Nto Egypt without being spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:48.45,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sign to let them \Nknow we want more tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.56,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you do this in Hong Kong, \Nthey'll bring you seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:01.57,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when they pour tea into your cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.87,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,This means "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:12.34,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.53,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a tourist from France,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:19.48,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm having a hard time \Nwith the kanji on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:21.22,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.99,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:27.69,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, Jotaro. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.13,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I've been to Hong Kong many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.93,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can at least read the kanji on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:43.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Food with shrimp, duck, \Nsharkfin, and mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.84,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have this, this, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.71,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:59.16,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,0)}Gong
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:59.17,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like food with beef, \Nfish, clams, and frog, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.16,JoJo-Names1,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(634,0)}Roasted Frog        Rice Porridge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.16,JoJo-Names3,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(634,0)}Clam Dish                                                    Stewed Fish
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.28,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. This is rather different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.43,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.44,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:14.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what you order.\NIt's all delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.23,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone, dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.41,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.12,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well? It's pretty good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:38.13,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they've certainly taken \Na lot of time to prepare this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.88,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Look, these carrots...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.47,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,They're shaped like stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.19,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.19,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:57.55,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I know has this \Nexact mark on their neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:08.23,JoJo-Rumble,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.23,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:05.42,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you another...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.79,JoJo-main,Avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.88,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:21.28,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:27.76,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.18,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Another Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.69,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,H-His sword is so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.67,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand holds The Chariot card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.20,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:52.33,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,Mohammed Avdol,\N it appears that you want to die first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:55.33,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a fire clock on that table!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:22:00.46,JoJo-main,dude,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you by the time \Nthat clock burns to twelve!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.02,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.84,JoJo-main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to be friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:39.97,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Something is bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:43.63,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Stick with me,\N and it'll disappear from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.94,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,That left arm is not a right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:47.63,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,To think you're trying to use
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.03,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,fortune-telling to fight a fortune teller...
